We weren't meant for each other.

35
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:58,716
- I couldn't see it.
- I don't remember it had anything...

36
00:14:02,544 --> 00:14:04,180
I don't know if I even loved her.

37
00:14:05,328 --> 00:14:06,580
Maybe I did.

38
00:14:07,842 --> 00:14:10,260
- What do you think?
- I don't know.

39
00:14:10,506 --> 00:14:13,397
I don't know the answer to that.
Do you ever talk to her?

40
00:14:14,053 --> 00:14:17,503
She called once and left a message.
I left her a message...

41
00:14:21,029 --> 00:14:23,379
Are you seeing anybody at the moment?

42
00:14:27,014 --> 00:14:28,664
